snippet.title: Johnny Depp looks fine in new photos after gaunt appearances with fans
snippet.description: The Hollywood Vampires  who are currently touring in Europe  posted photos of him on stage and behind the scenes with Guns N Roses bass guitarist Duff McKagan after Depp was pictured with fans looking thin and pale. Its unclear  though  if the photos are new.In the original photos  taken in Moscow after a show  the 54-year-old Depp looked sickly beneath oversized hats and sunglasses. While there was never an explanation given for his scary appearance  it sounds like there may not be anything wrong after all.Johnny is having a great time on the tour playing with the guys  a source told People  insisting that Depp is healthy.Depp has been performing with Alice Cooper and Aerosmiths Joe Perry in Hollywood Vampires since 2015.Last year  he and Amber Heard finalized an ugly divorce after the actress accused him of verbal and physical abuse  including an alleged drunken attack in which the "Pirates of the Caribbean" star hurled a cell phone at his wife and left her with a bruised face.Heard received $7 million in the divorce settlement and donated the money to charity.
